{"tid":2115380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔撚洗做] 水務署：停抄水錶","createTime":"2020-07-19T12:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T07:21:40.000Z","uid":77196,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b509415549f3dee19ad3c488b43dd9d4272ee3","tid":2115380,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200719/GALOBZUN4YJZRIPISZUDV7GWU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2FGALOBZUN4YJZRIPISZUDV7GWU4%2F&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8poTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=6ee7d814\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2FGALOBZUN4YJZRIPISZUDV7GWU4%2F&h=e2218195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200719/GALOBZUN4YJZRIPISZUDV7GWU4/</a><br />\n<br />\n之後果兩期水費單自己睇路喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f8bfafeb82a5806ba15b5f268c84b677462627","tid":2115380,"uid":168716,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/19/P2020071900666.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F19%2FP2020071900666.htm&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8poTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=fb066827\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/19/P2020071900666.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n例行抄讀水錶暫停，就用水周期在期間到期的帳戶，水務署會於帳戶的例行抄讀水錶恢復後，根據之前和最新實際水錶讀數，將有關用水周期合併計算用水量發出水費單。"},{"pid":"2547fa9f54b033d968e3d070842c33e051e6be5e","tid":2115380,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feb04fcafccc673718dee6b455223b25ac891fb8","tid":2115380,"uid":72633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"今期水費已經多咗一倍啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo